---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'Privacy Policy';
const description = 'Privacy policy for FreezerBatchCocktails.com';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <article class="py-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p><em>Last updated: January 2025</em></p>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>

        <h3>Email Addresses</h3>
        <p>
          If you subscribe to our newsletter, we collect your email address. We use this solely
          to send you new recipes, tips, and occasional product recommendations. We do not sell,
          rent, or share your email address with third parties.
        </p>
        <p>
          Every email includes an unsubscribe link. You can opt out at any time, and we'll
          remove your address from our list promptly.
        </p>

        <h3>Analytics</h3>
        <p>
          We may use privacy-respecting analytics (like Cloudflare Web Analytics) to understand
          how visitors use our site. This data is aggregated and does not identify you personally.
        </p>

        <h3>Cookies</h3>
        <p>
          This site does not use cookies for tracking. Your browser may store preferences locally
          (like your last-used recipe), but this data stays on your device.
        </p>

        <h2>Affiliate Links</h2>
        <p>
          Some links on this site are affiliate links to Amazon and other retailers. When you
          click these links, the retailer may set their own cookies. Please refer to their
          privacy policies for more information.
        </p>

        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> Hosts and serves this website</li>
          <li><strong>Amazon:</strong> Affiliate product links</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
          You can unsubscribe from our email list at any time using the link in any email,
          or by emailing us directly. We'll remove your address within 10 business days
          (usually much faster).
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about this policy? Email us at
          <a href="mailto:hello@freezerbatchcocktails.com">hello@freezerbatchcocktails.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
